</math>
<asciimath>ii(T)_{"meas"} = ii(T)_{90} ("TPW") + ii(A)("D") * ii(delta) "D" + ii(A)("O") * ii(delta) ""^{18}"O" + ii(A)(""^{17}"O") {ii(delta) ""^{17}"O" - [(1 + ii(delta) ""^{18}"O")^{0.528} -  1]} ,</asciimath></stem></formula>

<p id="_cbfe6b28-577e-f0b4-c491-16433e446c37">where the coefficient <stem type="MathML" block="false"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML">
